# =============================================================================
# .env/local.example -- Template for .env/local (Layer 5, gitignored)
#
# USAGE
# -----
#   cp .env/local.example .env/local
#   # Then fill in ASANA_PAT and ASANA_WORKSPACE_GID (see Secrets section below).
#
# Any variable set in .env/local overrides the same-named variable from
# .env/defaults (Layer 3). Layer-3 vars a dev may want to override here:
#   - ASANA_CW_ENVIRONMENT   (default: development)
#   - ASANA_CACHE_S3_BUCKET  (default: autom8-s3)
#   - ASANA_CACHE_S3_REGION  (default: us-east-1)
#
# =============================================================================
# 6-LAYER ENV LOADER PRECEDENCE
# Defined in scripts/a8-devenv.sh:_a8_load_env (lines 362-406).
# Later layers override earlier layers.
#
# Layer  File path                         Committed  Encrypted  Typical contents
# -----  --------------------------------  ---------  ---------  -----------------------------------------------
# 1      .a8/{org}/env.defaults            Yes        No         Ecosystem non-secrets (line 364)
# 2      .a8/{org}/secrets.shared          Yes        Yes        Ecosystem shared secrets (line 374)
# 3      .env/defaults                     Yes        No         Project non-secrets: S3 defaults, env name (line 377)
# 4      .env/secrets                      Yes        Yes        Project encrypted secrets (line 385)
# 5      .env/local  <-- THIS FILE         No         No         Local developer overrides, secrets (line 388)
# 6      .envrc.local                      No         No         Shell-level overrides, sourced by direnv (line 406)
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# SECRETS  (required -- fetch from AWS or fill in manually)
# =============================================================================
#
# Fetch all at once:
#   just fetch-secrets
#
# Or manually:
#   aws secretsmanager get-secret-value --secret-id "autom8y/asana/asana-pat" --query SecretString --output text
#   aws secretsmanager get-secret-value --secret-id "autom8y/asana/asana-workspace-gid" --query SecretString --output text
ASANA_PAT=REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ASANA_PAT
ASANA_WORKSPACE_GID=REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_WORKSPACE_GID

# =============================================================================
# CACHE / OFFLINE OVERRIDES  (optional -- commented out by default)
#
# These vars have Layer-3 defaults in .env/defaults. Uncomment and edit only
# if you need to target a different bucket or region than the project default.
# =============================================================================

# Uncomment to override Layer 3 default `autom8-s3` -- see .env/defaults
# ASANA_CACHE_S3_BUCKET=your-personal-dev-bucket

# Uncomment to override Layer 3 default `us-east-1` -- see .env/defaults
# ASANA_CACHE_S3_REGION=us-east-1

# Uncomment for LocalStack (see docker-compose.override.yml:34 for the compose value)
# ASANA_CACHE_S3_ENDPOINT_URL=http://localstack:4566

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: LocalStack compose target
#
# To hit the docker-compose LocalStack instead of real AWS, set:
#   ASANA_CACHE_S3_ENDPOINT_URL=http://localstack:4566
#   ASANA_CACHE_S3_BUCKET=autom8-s3
#
# Both values are already configured in docker-compose.override.yml for the
# containerised CLI path. The overrides above are only needed for host-side runs.
# =============================================================================
